name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
    t1.CREATEDATE,
    t1.DOMAINS,
    t1.ENABLE,
    t1.ISVALID,
    t1.ORGCODE,
    t1.ORGID,
    t1.ORGLEVEL,
    t1.ORGNAME,
    t1.SAASMODE,
    t1.SHORTNAME,
    t1.SHOWORDER,
    t1.SRFDCID,
    t1.UPDATEDATE
FROM (SELECT
          t1.CREATE_TIME as CREATEDATE,
          t1.DC as DOMAINS,
          t1.ENABLED as ENABLE,
          t1.ENABLED as ISVALID,
          t1.ORGANIZATION_NUMBER as ORGCODE,
          t1.ID as ORGID,
          1 as ORGLEVEL,
          t1.ORGANIZATION_NAME as ORGNAME,
          t1.PARENT_ID as PORGID,
          0 as SAASMODE,
          t1.ORGANIZATION_NAME as SHORTNAME,
          t1.SORT as SHOWORDER,
          t1.UPDATE_TIME as UPDATEDATE,
          t1.DC as SRFDCID
      FROM sys_organization t1) t1
